---
// HowWeHelp.astro - How We Help section showcasing FiNAN's main service areas
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-5xl">
        Our Advocacy
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        FiNAN supports Filipino nurses in the Nordics through guidance,
        advocacy, and community building. Explore our main focus areas and find
        resources tailored to your needs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Licensing Guidance Card -->
      <div
        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-900"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/icons/placeholder-icon.svg"
              alt="Licensing Guidance Icon"
              class="h-6 w-6 brightness-0 invert filter"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Licensing Guidance
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Get step-by-step support for obtaining or renewing your Nordic RN
          license, tailored to each country's specific requirements. FiNAN
          provides clear, reliable information to help you navigate the process
          with confidence.
        </p>

        <!-- Link -->
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-gray-900 transition-colors hover:text-gray-700"
        >
          Licensing Guidance
          <svg
            class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Cultural Integration Card -->
      <div
        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/icons/placeholder-icon.svg"
              alt="Cultural Integration Icon"
              class="h-6 w-6 brightness-0 invert filter"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Cultural Integration
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Receive dedicated support to help you adapt and thrive in life across
          the Nordic region. FiNAN offers resources for learning the local
          language, understanding cultural norms, and connecting with community
          networks.
        </p>

        <!-- Link -->
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-gray-900 transition-colors hover:text-gray-700"
        >
          Cultural Integration
          <svg
            class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Policy Advocacy Card -->
      <div
        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/icons/placeholder-icon.svg"
              alt="Policy Advocacy Icon"
              class="h-6 w-6 brightness-0 invert filter"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Policy Advocacy</h3>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          We actively collaborate with government policymakers, hospitals,
          healthcare institutions, and universities to improve the recognition
          of Filipino nurses' qualifications and enhance their professional
          well-being.
        </p>

        <!-- Link -->
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-gray-900 transition-colors hover:text-gray-700"
        >
          Policy Advocacy
          <svg
            class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
